msgid ""
"Every :file:`records.config` configuration variable can be overridden by "
"a corresponding environment variable. This can be useful in situations "
"where you need a static :file:`records.config` but still want to tweak "
"one or two settings. The override variable is formed by converting the "
":file:`records.config` variable name to upper case, and replacing any dot"
" separators with an underscore."
msgstr ""

