"domain name"
msgstr ""

# 972409c206304311a70dd386afb9f577
#: ../../admin-guide/files/records.config.en.rst:1827
msgid ""
"Traffic Server can attempt to resolve unqualified hostnames by expanding "
"to the local domain. For example if a client makes a request to an "
"unqualified host (``host_x``) and the Traffic Server local domain is "
"``y.com`` , then Traffic Server will expand the hostname to "
"``host_x.y.com``."
msgstr ""

# 1094fcacbfac4f0aac6d1b691f2d591e
#: ../../admin-guide/files/records.config.en.rst:1836
msgid ""
