" a background fetch for the new data."
msgstr ""

# 3547b74c9ad44e3e8b223b280d6211c8
#: ../../admin-guide/files/records.config.en.rst:1902
msgid "If not set then stale records are not served."
msgstr ""

# d43ea5f4a8c6487a84fb0b8758239864
#: ../../admin-guide/files/records.config.en.rst:1907
msgid ""
"The amount of space (in bytes) used to store ``hostdb``. The value of "
"this variable must be increased if you increase the size of the "
"`proxy.config.hostdb.size`_ variable."
msgstr ""

# 8cdd8cb0a9ed49419e5fecd15034f757
#: ../../admin-guide/files/records.config.en.rst:1913
msgid "The maximum number of entries that can be stored in the database."
msgstr ""

# 99d229e7045e4294b165f1cffa2c55fc
#: ../../admin-guide/files/records.config.en.rst:1917
msgid ""
"For values above ``200000``, you must increase "
":ts:cv:`proxy.config.hostdb.storage_size` by at least 44 bytes per entry."
msgstr ""

# 6747377bc5cc4d71ac9560904461f4e6
#: ../../admin-guide/files/records.config.en.rst:1922
msgid ""
"A host entry will eventually time out and be discarded. This variable "
"controls how that time is calculated. A DNS request will return a TTL "
"value and an internal value can be set with "
":ts:cv:`proxy.config.hostdb.timeout`. This variable determines which "
"value will be used."
msgstr ""

# 0fc1dc78ff9a4c3ba66d5076d12c55ac
#: ../../admin-guide/files/records.config.en.rst:1927
msgid "TTL"
msgstr ""

# 8f55702b679948a4b3403b160daf264d
#: ../../admin-guide/files/records.config.en.rst:1929
msgid "The TTL from the DNS response."
msgstr ""

# f3fb66e9cdfd4e9780c998f9c04fff55
#: ../../admin-guide/files/records.config.en.rst:1930
msgid "The internal timeout value."
msgstr ""

# 204a8fd95a7f4ec28ca1ca296e523d21
#: ../../admin-guide/files/records.config.en.rst:1931
msgid ""
"The smaller of the DNS and internal TTL values. The internal timeout "
"value becomes a maximum TTL."
msgstr ""

# 133e7a22f7894e0dbe0691c289d85cfc
#: ../../admin-guide/files/records.config.en.rst:1932
msgid ""
"The larger of the DNS and internal TTL values. The internal timeout value"
" become a minimum TTL."
msgstr ""

# 84fdba42c8cc41dfb4c392f96b2562f6
