# 0ef0732fe2104d8aa4e7c439670e8839
#: ../../admin-guide/files/records.config.en.rst:1941
msgid "See :ts:cv:`proxy.config.hostdb.ttl_mode` for when this value is used."
msgstr ""

# 8e80414483e64a8baf860478663ca884
#: ../../admin-guide/files/records.config.en.rst:1946
msgid "Set host resolution to use strict round robin."
msgstr ""

# 2135e34107984eab85dc0ae4b54883d1
#: ../../admin-guide/files/records.config.en.rst:1948
msgid ""
"When this and :ts:cv:`proxy.config.hostdb.timed_round_robin` are both "
"disabled (set to ``0``), Traffic Server always uses the same origin "
"server for the same client, for as long as the origin server is "
"available. Otherwise if this is set then IP address is rotated on every "
"request. This setting takes precedence over "
":ts:cv:`proxy.config.hostdb.timed_round_robin`."
msgstr ""

# d7800cbbbd7c47fbaba2b3289db7db5d
#: ../../admin-guide/files/records.config.en.rst:1956
msgid "Set host resolution to use timed round robin."
msgstr ""

# 53ed8f41f1374ebb94fff472ffa06986
#: ../../admin-guide/files/records.config.en.rst:1958
msgid ""
"When this and :ts:cv:`proxy.config.hostdb.strict_round_robin` are both "
"disabled (set to ``0``), Traffic Server always uses the same origin "
"server for the same client, for as long as the origin server is "
"available. Otherwise if this is set to :arg:`N` the IP address is rotated"
" if more than :arg:`N` seconds have past since the first time the current"
" address was used."
msgstr ""

# 0fa23a173e6b456a8d42c983faa7b199
#: ../../admin-guide/files/records.config.en.rst:1965
msgid "Set the file path for an external host file."
msgstr ""

# 8725cce20c1643e795d4d4505ef5f283
#: ../../admin-guide/files/records.config.en.rst:1967
msgid ""
"If this is set (non-empty) then the file is presumed to be a hosts file "
"in the standard `host file format "
"<http://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc1123#page-13>`_. It is read and the "
"entries there added to the HostDB. The file is periodically checked for a"
" more recent modification date in which case it is reloaded. The interval"
" is set by the value :ts:cv:`proxy.config.hostdb.host_file.interval`."
msgstr ""

# be5a51aec3f64aa486f4c8d3f25ba83d
#: ../../admin-guide/files/records.config.en.rst:1969
msgid ""
"While not technically reloadable, the value is read every time the file "
"is to be checked so that if changed the new value will be used on the "
"next check and the file will be treated as modified."
msgstr ""

# d30fcb2d5f954edb8e778e5b03c7d0d5
#: ../../admin-guide/files/records.config.en.rst:1976
msgid ""
"Set the file changed check timer for "
":ts:cv:`proxy.config.hostdb.host_file.path`."
msgstr ""

# a68d895464e5459391a001afd9148d88
#: ../../admin-guide/files/records.config.en.rst:1978
msgid ""
"The file is checked every this many seconds to see if it has changed. If "
"so the HostDB is updated with the new values in the file."
msgstr ""

