"adding the Strict-Transport-Security header.  The value is in seconds. A "
"value of ``0`` will set the max-age value to ``0`` and should remove the "
"HSTS entry from the client.  A value of ``-1`` will disable this feature "
"and not set the header.  This option is only used for HTTPS requests and "
"the header will not be set on HTTP requests."
msgstr ""

# ee7d178b535b46f9b8d7c082577096fe
#: ../../admin-guide/files/records.config.en.rst:2548
